race.comment: GOOFINATOR (6) has put together back-to-back placings after scoring three back at Goulburn, most recently beaten narrowly at Dubbo. Is ticking along nicely and only needs to hold his form to take this out. OWN THEM (1) finished a narrow fourth two runs back in a hot form race at Goulburn then went a few better last start to score at Canberra. Ticking along superbly now and can repeat the dose on the quick back-up. MR TADASHI (2) was in a different class last time with a dominant all-the-way win here on the main track. Tougher this time but has to be taken seriously off that. DREAMSTONE (5) has failed to go on with the job in his last two but has plenty of early toe and should give another bold sight. Don't dismiss.
